@node Controls "How to control"

				@{b}Controls of game@{ub}

	@{b}WBTRIZ@{ub} use @{b}Joystick@{ub} or @{b}Keyboard...@{ub} (Check menu)

	@{b}Default keyboards@{ub}

	@{b}CRS_LEFT@{ub} ..................... Move to left
	@{b}CRS_PRGHT@{ub} .................... Move to right
	@{b}CRS_DOWN@{ub} ..................... Move to down
	@{b}SPACEBAR@{ub} ..................... Move to down very fast
	@{b}RSHIFT@{ub} ....................... Rotation of block (left)
	@{b}CONTROL@{ub} ...................... Rotation of block (right)

	Keyboards is editable to menu.
	Look at my @{"RAWSTATUS" LINK RSTAT} code...

	For example (CRS_UP) = ($4c)


