@node technical "Technical info"

				@{b}TECHNICAL INFO:@{ub}

	- Commodities support
	- Datatypes support (Graphic block must same size)
	- Scandir gfx/sfx, sort it and create menu.
	- Auto detect size of brush.
	- Max gfx/sfx filename in menu is @{b}5000@{ub}
	- Max store motion move is @{b}100000@{ub}
	- Sample only @{b}8SVX@{ub}
	- Crunch @{b}replay@{ub} using @{b}xpk compressors@{ub}

	If new datatype remap procedure is problem... (No Transparency)
	Then change first colour (for @{b}default@{ub} gfx) in wbpalette to:
	@{b}R=140,G=140,B=140@{ub} or change all gfx background colour to
	your first wbpalette!...   Sorry, @{b}maby@{ub} fix it, in future...

	When play replay, look at @{b}ABOUT@{ub} menu... (Finish in procent.)
	If you need proportional block (@{b}default@{ub} for @{b}HIRES@{ub}) then use menu:
	@{b}"Edit/Block Scale/Scale for Y"@{ub} (Add @{b}8@{ub} for @{b}default@{ub} to @{b}HIRESLACED@{ub})
@endnode

